      'guide_tip_title': 'Tip for Best Result', 'guide_tip_desc': 'To ensure the camera recognizes the sign accurately and quickly, make the (hand pose) clear and at chest level, ensuring good lighting in the place.\n\nIf you notice the camera stopped recognizing for a while, simply close the camera and reopen it to resume working efficiently.',
      'guide_home_title': 'Main Interface', 'guide_home_desc': 'Your quick gateway to the world of sign language in the ArSL interpreter app, and it includes two main options:',
      'guide_home_rec_desc': 'To open the camera and start instant translation of sign language with a steady hand pose into texts.', 'guide_home_learn_desc': 'Your visual guide to explore the sign dictionary and test your skills.',
      'guide_smart_trans_title': 'Smart Translation (Camera Recognition)', 'guide_smart_start': 'Start Translation', 'guide_smart_start_desc': 'Select the sign type (alphabets, numbers, or sentences) to let the camera start reading your hand pose in real-time.',
      'guide_smart_privacy': 'Security and Privacy', 'guide_smart_privacy_desc': 'Translation is instant and done entirely inside your device without saving or sending any data. To ensure your privacy is protected, the app prevents screen capturing while the camera is running.',
      'guide_smart_age': 'Age Input', 'guide_smart_age_desc': 'When making the (My Age) sign and it is recognized, the app will ask you to enter a number. You can perform two consecutive numbers quickly, or perform just one number and wait a little for the time bar to complete to be adopted.', 'guide_smart_age_note': '-The current age display mechanism relies on separate numbers - it is a temporary solution until developed.',
      'guide_smart_voice': 'Translation and Pronunciation', 'guide_smart_voice_desc': 'You can use the (Google Translate) button to convert the recognized text to your preferred language (can be changed from settings), and press the (Speaker) button to listen to the audio pronunciation of the sign.',
      'guide_smart_save': 'Documenting Conversations (Save)', 'guide_smart_save_desc': 'The app provides a save button (top of the screen) that allows you to write down the detected texts and written replies with their translations, and keep them directly in the (History) so you can refer to them at any time.',
      'guide_smart_front': 'Front Camera', 'guide_smart_front_desc': 'To ensure recognition when using the front camera, you will be asked to flip the phone upside down, and the screen will return to normal once you switch back to the back camera.',
      'guide_smart_ain': 'Note for letter (ع)', 'guide_smart_ain_desc': 'When performing the sign for the letter (ع - Ain), try to keep your hand slightly away from your chest to avoid confusing it with the (My Name) sign.',
      'guide_learn_title': 'Learning and Tests', 'guide_learn_desc': 'Your ideal place to develop your skills:',
      'guide_learn_browse': 'Browse and Save Signs', 'guide_learn_browse_desc': 'You can browse the sign images clearly, and press download image from the top of the screen to download to your phone\'s gallery.',
      'guide_learn_attempts': 'Attempts System', 'guide_learn_attempts_desc': 'You have 3 chances to answer each question. The correct answer from the first time gives you a green mark, a festive pop, and encouragement (you can stop the pop from the settings). Attempts decrease upon mistakes without decreasing your score. (Only skipping the question or running out of attempts makes you lose its score).',
      'guide_learn_auto': 'Auto Navigation', 'guide_learn_auto_desc': 'For a smooth experience, the app will move to the next question automatically after you answer in (4 seconds), and you can turn it off from the settings.',
      'guide_learn_cam': 'Perform Sign (Camera)', 'guide_learn_cam_desc': 'The third test opens by default on the front camera (and you can switch to the back). The app gives you a preparation timeout (\'Get ready to start\') before each question so you can read it and prepare your hand.',
      'guide_learn_score': 'Score Distribution and Challenge', 'guide_learn_score_desc': 'Calculates the score (out of 100%):',
      'guide_learn_score_letters': 'Alphabets (32 questions): 3.12 points per question, and upon completing the challenge increase by (5 questions) to make the total 37 questions, the question score becomes 2.70 points.',
      'guide_learn_score_numbers': 'Numbers (10 questions): 10 points per question, and upon completing the challenge increase by (5 questions) to make the total 15 questions, the question score becomes 6.66 points.',
      'guide_learn_score_sentences': 'Sentences (25 questions): 4 points per question, and upon completing the challenge increase by (10 questions) to make the total 35 questions, the question score becomes 2.85 points.',
      'guide_settings_title': 'Customization and Settings', 'guide_settings_desc': 'We designed the app to suit your personal preferences:',
      'guide_settings_theme': 'Appearance and Languages', 'guide_settings_theme_desc': 'Switch between night and day mode, and choose your preferred language from 10 global languages.',
      'guide_settings_theme_sub': 'If you choose "Japanese" for example, the app interface will change to Japanese, and the (Google Translate) button will convert the detected Arabic text from the camera or reply box to Japanese. And vice versa, as texts written in Japanese are translated to Arabic.',
      'guide_settings_text': 'Text and Audio Customization', 'guide_settings_text_desc': 'Control the font size of the recognized text or the reply box, and adjust the audio pronunciation speed of the text.',
      'guide_settings_test': 'Test Settings', 'guide_settings_test_desc': 'The ability to enable/disable automatic navigation between questions, and festive pop effects.',
      'guide_settings_alert_desc': 'Enable vibration or sound to notify you as soon as the app successfully captures the sign from the camera.',
      'guide_video_title': 'Video Tutorial', 'guide_video_ar': 'Arabic Tutorial:', 'guide_video_en': 'English Tutorial:',

